---
title: Mediterranean-Inspired Chicken Breasts and Veggies with Orzo and Sun-Dried Tomato Pesto
description: This sheet pan dinner is loaded with bold Mediterranean flavours and is oh-so-simple to make. After a bit of prep, the oven does most of the work and you'll end up with a feast for the eyes and the taste buds!
